df = inputs[0]
df['temp']=0
for i in range(len(df)):
	if df['time'][i]=='_07시' or df['time'][i]=='_08시' or df['time'][i]=='_16시' or df['time'][i]=='_17시' or df['time'][i]=='_18시' :
		df['temp'][i] =1
	else:
		df['temp'][i] =2
		
		

df['interval_new'] =0.0
for i in range(len(df)):
	if df['temp'][i] == 1:
		df['interval_new'][i] = df['interval'][i] *0.74
	else:
		df['interval_new'][i] = df['interval'][i] *1.1
		
		
df['count'] = 60 / df['interval']
df['count_new'] = 60 / df['interval_new']
df['output'] = df['sum'] / df['count']
df['output2'] = df['sum'] / df['count_new']

param.script:
#
#   NOTE : Enter "Out Table Alias"
#   ex)
#       inputDataframe = inputs[0]
#       result = inputDataframe
#
df = inputs[0]
df['interval_diff'] =0.0
df['profit'] =0.0
df['loss'] =0.0
df['total_m']=0.0


for i in range(len(df)):
	if df['temp'][i] == 1:
		df['interval_diff'][i] = df['interval'][i] - df['interval_new'][i]
		df['profit'][i] = (df['interval_diff'][i]/60) * 8350
		df['loss'][i]=0
		df['total_m'][i]=df['profit'][i]*df['sum'][i]
	elif df['temp'][i] == 2:
		df['interval_diff'][i] = df['interval_new'][i] - df['interval'][i]
		df['loss'][i] = (df['interval_diff'][i]/60) * 8350
		df['profit'][i]=0
		df['total_m'][i]=df['loss'][i]*df['sum'][i]
	else:
		df['interval_diff'][i]=0
		df['profit'][i]=0
		df['loss'][i]=0
		df['total_m'][i]=0
